Node.Notes: Uncertain. Could mean this [lamb] is the Passover [lamb] to Yahweh or this day/practice is the Passover to Yahweh.
Since the Hebrews count days from sundown to sundown, the evening of 14th day counts as the start of the 15th day and so it is 7 days to the evening of the 21st day.
Uncertain. Assumes: The men were about six hundred thousand ones going on foot, besides children.
Uncertain. Some take on foot and the men together as strong men on foot. (the protective, fighting force).
Uncertain. Most take in sense of dependents and translate women and children. Perhaps verse counts men strong enough for battle and indicates male children not yet old/strong enough to fight. here
Exact nature of the mixed multitude uncertain. What is clear is that they are other people that are not considered Israelites.
